    "properties_description": "The main therapeutic properties of Cornopteris parvisora are its anti-inflammatory activity, which provides relief from redness and swelling in the body. The analgesic property of this plant helps to alleviate pain, reducing the discomfort associated with various health conditions. The antimicrobial property of Cornopteris parvisora is effective in combating bacterial and fungal infections, promoting wound healing and preventing the spread of diseases. The antioxidant property of this plant helps to neutralize free radicals, protecting the body from oxidative stress and cell damage. The antiviral property of Cornopteris parvisora is beneficial in preventing the replication of viruses, reducing the severity of viral infections.",
